steps.html_instructions:
Slight left onto Ali Dirikoç Blv./Kayseri Cd./D765
Continue to follow Kayseri Cd./D765

At the roundabout, take the 3rd exit onto Avanos Gülşehir Yolu

Continue to follow Kozaklı Şefaatli Yolu

Turn right onto Kırıkkale Yozgat Yolu/D200/E88
Continue to follow D200/E88

Turn left onto Çorum Yozgat Yolu/D795
Continue to follow D795

Continue onto Çorum Çankırı Yolu/D795
Continue to follow D795
At the roundabout, take the 4th exit and stay on Osmancık Cd.
Continue straight to stay on Çorum Cd.

Turn left onto Ömer Derindere Blv./İstanbul Samsun Yolu/D100/E80
Continue to follow İstanbul Samsun Yolu/D100/E80
Continue straight to stay on Boyabat Tosya Yolu/D785

Turn left onto Boyabat Havza Yolu/D030
Continue to follow D030

Merge onto Sinop Bafra Yolu/D010

At the roundabout, take the 2nd exit onto Derviş Sarabil Cd.
